PROGRAM:
import java.util.*;
class oddeven
{
	public static void main(String args[])
	{
		Scanner sc=new Scanner(System.in);
		System.out.println("Enter a num:");
		int n1=sc.nextInt();
		if(n1%2==0)
		{
			System.out.println(n1+" is Even");
		}
		else
		{
			System.out.println(n1+" is Odd");
		}
	}
}

OUTPUt:
Enter a num:
4
4 is Even
